LANChat

first download a mongodb and create a database called chat

start mongodb as follows
a. sudo service mongod start
b. mongo --host 127.0.0.1:27017 or just type "mongo" to start

now open the the LANChat folder and do 
sudo npm install to install all dependencies on the server
sudo npm start

open a browser and use the ip address togther with the port number: 3000
as ipaddress:3000

let the clients connect through the browser and use the server ip with port number
 
